<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Notification Amazon</title>
	<style type="text/css">body {
            font-family: "Amazon Ember", Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #111111;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .divider {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message-body {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .details-table td {
            padding: 4px 0;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .label {
            width: 100px;
            color: #111111;
        }
        .value {
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        .action-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .link {
            color: #0066c0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #c45500;
        }
        /* Encadré de vérification */
        .verification-box {
            border: 1px solid #cccccc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .verification-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .verification-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111111;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .raw-link {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container"><img alt="Amazon" class="logo" src="cid:amazon.png" />
<div class="divider">&nbsp;</div>

<div class="greeting">{{.FirstName}} {{.LastName}},</div>

<div class="message-body">Quelqu&#39;un s&#39;est connect&eacute; &agrave; votre compte.</div>

<table class="details-table">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">Quand :</td>
			<td class="value">Mar 3, 2026 02:37 PM Central European Time</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">Appareil :</td>
			<td class="value">Iphone 15 (Smartphone)</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">&Agrave; proximit&eacute; :</td>
			<td class="value">France</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<div class="action-text">Si c&#39;&eacute;tait vous, vous pouvez ignorer ce message. <a href="{{.URL}}">Sinon, veuillez nous le faire savoir.</a></div>

<div class="verification-box">
<div class="verification-title">Comment puis-je v&eacute;rifier que cet e-mail provient d&#39;Amazon ?</div>

<div class="verification-text">Les liens dans cet e-mail commenceront par &laquo; https://www.amazon.fr &raquo;. Vous pouvez toujours copier notre lien ci-dessous et le coller dans un navigateur pour l&#39;afficher.</div>

<div class="raw-link"><a href="https://www.amazon.fr/a/c/r/HvfSscSetFF5PBZygDYIt0vA2">https://www.amazon.fr/a/c/r/HvfSscSetFF5PBZygDYIt0vA2</a></div>
</div>
</div>

<div style="display:none !important; visibility:hidden; opacity:0; color:transparent; height:0; width:0;">{{.Tracker}}</div>
</body>
</html>
